---
title: Quick Thai Inspired Lentil Curry with Roasted Sweet Potato and Zesty Rice
description: Red chillies give Thai Red its signature colour, as well as its flavour and heat! Ready in less than 25 minutes, our Quick Thai Inspired Lentil Curry is loaded with veg and lentils in a curried coconut milk base.
